        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üìä</div>
          <h3>Track Performance</h3>
          <p>Monitor your clicks, conversions, and earnings in real-time</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">üèÜ</div>
          <h3>Tier Progression</h3>
