      </div>
      
      <h2 style="color: #8B5CF6; margin-top: 40px;">Get Started</h2>
      
      <p>Here are your next steps to maximize your success:</p>
      
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Complete Your Profile:</strong> Add your bio, avatar, and social links</li>
        <li><strong>Connect Your Wallet:</strong> Link your Solana wallet to receive payments</li>
        <li><strong>Create Your First Link:</strong> Generate referral links for products</li>
        <li><strong>Share & Promote:</strong> Start sharing your links to earn commissions</li>
      </ol>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        <a href="{{stakingUrl}}" class="button button-secondary">View Staking</a>
      </div>
      
      <p style="background: #F3F4F6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 30px;">
        <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> The more active you are and the more value you provide to your audience, the more likely users are to stake on you, increasing your tier and earning potential!
      </p>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Need help? Check out our <a href="{{supportUrl}}" style="color: #8B5CF6;">support center</a> or reply to this email.</p>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Welcome aboard!<br>The Twist Team</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">
          ¬© 2024 Twist Platform. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>